Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
timing_set_nsigma_multiplier(25.10)        timing_set_nsigma_multiplier(25.10)

Name
       timing_set_nsigma_multiplier

Syntax
       timing_set_nsigma_multiplier <value>

       Default: 3

       Controls the sigma multiplier to be used in SOCV mode.

       This  global  variable  allows a single N value for both setup and hold
       reporting. For example,

       set timing_set_nsigma_multiplier 4.5

       To set this global variable, use the set command.

       Note: The timing_set_nsigma_multiplier global variable is obsolete  and
       has  been  replaced  with the set_socv_reporting_nsigma_multiplier com-
       mand.  You   can   use   this   global   variable   by   setting   tim-
       ing_socv_view_based_nsigma_multiplier_mode to false. For future compat-
       ibility,  you  should  migrate  your  scripts to use the new view-based
       methodology.

